# KAPI PEN — Phase 4 Customer Account System Documentation

## Phase Overview

Phase 4 focused on implementing a production-ready Customer Account System on top of the completed Authentication infrastructure from Phase 3.

This phase provides authenticated users with a personalized account experience including profile management, address management, order history, and persistent cart ownership.

