## 2. Profile Management

### Route

```text
/account/profile
```

### Features

* Fetch authenticated user from Prisma

* Display:

  * First Name
  * Last Name
  * Email
  * Account Creation Date

* Inline profile editing

* Supabase metadata synchronization

* Prisma user synchronization

### Files

```text
app/(store)/account/(dashboard)/profile/

lib/actions/auth/update-profile.ts
```

---

