## 4. Cart Ownership & Persistence

### Objective

Convert guest cart into authenticated user cart.

### Features

* User-owned cart records
* Persistent cart across sessions
* Persistent cart across devices
* Guest cart merging on login
* Database synchronization

### Database Models

```prisma
Cart
CartItem
```

### Files

```text
lib/actions/cart.ts

lib/store/cart-store.ts

components/store/auth/AuthProvider.tsx
```

### Flow

```text
Guest Cart
      ↓
User Login
      ↓
Merge Guest Cart
      ↓
Database Cart
      ↓
Persist Across Sessions
```

